title: Men's 3D Wolf Printed Hoodie
body_html:
Unleash your wild side with this Men’s 3D Wolf Printed Hoodie. Made from high-quality polyester, this hoodie features a fierce, eye-catching wolf design that pops with incredible detail. Perfect for animal lovers and those looking to make a bold statement, it’s comfortable, durable, and ideal for everyday wear.

✨ Features:

  • 3D Wolf print for a bold and captivating design
  • Premium polyester fabric (91%-99% polyester) for softness and durability
  • Comfortable and breathable – perfect for casual outings or cozy days at home
  • Standard fit – great for layering or wearing on its own
  • Vibrant and detailed print that stands out in any crowd

Size Information:

  • Please refer to the size chart for precise measurements. Since Asian sizes are smaller than European and American sizes, it's recommended to choose one size up if you're between sizes.

Package Includes:

  •  1 x 3D Wolf Printed Hoodie
